Definition: or `explode') if a particular condition is satisfied
Example: when exploded it may delete or corrupt data, or print a spurious message, or have other harmful effects; a disgruntled employee planted a logic bomb
Synonyms: slag_code, malevolent_program, a, set, of, instructions, inserted, into, program, that, are, designed, to, execute, or, explode, if, particular, condition, is, satisfied, when, exploded, it, may, delete, corrupt, data, print, spurious, message, have, other, harmful, effects, disgruntled, employee, planted, logic, bomb
Category: noun.communication
